Pre-Game Insights: To finish off their tour of Australia, the West Indies will take on the host nation in three T20 internationals in February.
The Windies journey to Australia will be forever remembered for their first Test win in the region for 27 years in Brisbane.
The second T20 is held in ACDT (6:30pm start) and the third in AWST (4pm start).
Miscellaneous Highlights: Every match of Australia's summer of cricket - including Tests, ODIs and T20Is - will be broadcast live on Fox Cricket and streamed on Kayo Sports.
